  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Two-Year Disease Free Survival Rate of Stage IB~IIIA adenocarcinoma after Adjuvant
      Chemotherapy with Pemetrexed and Cisplatin will be assessed. A total of 106 patients will be
      recruited for 12 months, and followed for two years, thus the duration of study will be 36
      months.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Primary endpoint : 2 year disease free survival

      Secondary endpoints:

      Overall survival, Frequency and severity of adverse events
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
